  title: Why create a `SceneLoader` static class?
  text: "It centralizes scene-loading logic, enforces the use of enums instead of
    strings, and reduces the risk of typos or hard-to-debug loading errors. It\u2019s
    a clean and scalable way to manage scene transitions. And making it static just
    ensures all the class members are marked as static."
